.Dd April 1, 2013
.Dt HEXCHAT 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm hexchat
.Nd a GTK+2 Internet Relay Chat client
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl acden
.Op Fl \-display Ns = Ns Ar display
.Op Fl \-minimize Ns = Ns Ar level
.Op Ar URL
.Sh DESCRIPTION
HexChat is a UTF-8 compatible Internet Relay Chat (IRC) client with a graphical
user interface.
.Pp
The user documentation is
.Lk https://hexchat.readthedocs.io/ here .
.Sh OPTIONS
.Ss Run options
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl a , \-no-auto
Disable auto connect to servers
.It Fl c , \-command Ns = Ns Ar command
Execute
.Ar command
.It Fl d , \-cfgdir Ns = Ns Ar path
Use a different config directory
.It Fl \-display Ns = Ns Ar display
X11 display to use
.It Fl e , \-existing
Open URL, or execute command, in a running HexChat
.It Fl \-minimize Ns = Ns Ar num
Set initial minimization: 0 normal, 1 iconified, 2 systray
.It Fl n , \-no-plugins
Disable auto load of plugins
.It Fl \-url Ns = Ns Ar url
Open an irc://server:port/channel?key URL
.El
.Ss Show-and-exit options
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl p , \-plugindir
Show plugin auto-load directory
.It Fl u , \-configdir
Show user config directory
.It Fl v , \-version
Show version information
.It Fl h , \-help
Show help options
.It Fl \-help-gtk
Show GTK+ options
.It Fl \-help-all
Show all help options
.El
.Sh HISTORY
HexChat is based on the older XChat client.
